<p class="wikiPara">
I've updated <a href="/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart3" target="" class="regularLink">Part 3</a> and <a href="/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart11" target="" class="regularLink">Part 11</a> of <a href="http://in.relation.to/tag/Introduction+to+Ceylon" target="" class="regularLink">Introduction to Ceylon</a> to incorporate some recent revisions to the language and <a href="http://in.relation.to/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart3#H-AmbiguitiesInMixinInheritance" target="" class="regularLink">fill in</a> some <a href="http://in.relation.to/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart11#H-SelfReferencesAndOuterInstanceReferences" target="" class="regularLink">missing details</a>. I've also added <a href="http://in.relation.to/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart3#H-IntroductionComparedToExtensionMethodsAndImplicitTypeConversions" target="" class="regularLink">some extra material</a> explaining <a href="http://in.relation.to/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart11#H-MultipleInheritanceAndQlinearizationq" target="" class="regularLink">the reasoning behind</a> a couple of the important decisions we've made.
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
UPDATE: I've also update <a href="/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart8" target="" class="regularLink">Part 8</a> to add <a href="http://in.relation.to/Bloggers/IntroductionToCeylonPart8#H-FunctionReferences" target="" class="regularLink">some missing information</a>.</p>
